            <p class="sidebar-md-desc hidden-lg hidden-xs">While they&#039;re both great smartphones, the iPhone 13 Pro massively impresses, but we&#039;re underwhelmed with the improvements Apple made year-over-year to the larger iPhone 13 Pro Max.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</article>
